data.description: Charming home with a Studio located in Montebello's most desirable residential neighborhood, near shopping, and transportation.  The front home offers a three-bedroom, one-bath.,  beautiful fireplace in the living room with plantation shutters.   and formal dining room.  The kitchen has a dishwasher and plenty of cabinet space.   The rear house is a Studio that features a combo living, a long driveway leads to the garage. This property is ideal for those multi-family living.
